SubjectLoran Station Baffin Island 1954 Termination of Treaty (US) #2
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America regarding the Construction and Operation of a Loran Station by the United States Coast Guard at Cape Christian, Baffin Island, done on 1st and 3 May 1954.
